---
import Layout from '../components/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="サービス | BizSys 現場改善システム" description="中小企業向けに業務システムの設計・開発・運用を一貫サポート。費用相場や進め方の無料相談受付中。Webアプリ・在庫管理・帳票・CSV連携など現場に合わせた開発をします。">

  <style is:global>
    /* ====================================================
       サービスページ共通
       ==================================================== */
    .svc-section { padding: 48px 0; }
    .svc-section h2 {
      text-align: left;
      font-size: 28px;
      font-weight: 800;
      color: #003b78;
      margin: 0 0 28px;
      line-height: 1.3;
    }

    /* ====================================================
       ヒーロー
       ==================================================== */
    .svc-hero {
      background: #F8F8F6;
      padding: 48px 0;
      overflow: hidden;
    }
    .svc-hero-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1.03fr 1fr;
      align-items: start;
      gap: 38px;
    }
    .svc-eyebrow {
      display: inline-block;
      background: #eaf2fa;
      color: #003b78;
      font-size: 16px;
      font-weight: 900;
      padding: 4px 16px;
      border-radius: 7px;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }
    .svc-hero h1 {
      font-size: 38px;
      line-height: 1.35;
      font-weight: 900;
      margin: 0 0 24px;
      color: #071225;
    }
    .sp-only { display: none; }
    .svc-hero h1 span { color: #0b4a93; }
    .svc-hero .lead {
      font-size: 17px;
      font-weight: 700;
      line-height: 1.8;
      margin: 0 0 28px;
      color: #071225;
    }
    .svc-hero-points {
      display: flex;
      gap: 28px;
      margin-bottom: 32px;
    }
    .svc-point {
      border-left: 5px solid #0b56a6;
      padding-left: 14px;
    }
    .svc-point strong { display: block; font-size: 18px; color: #071225; font-weight: 900; }
    .svc-point small  { display: block; font-size: 14px; color: #555; }
    .svc-hero-actions { display: flex; gap: 20px; flex-wrap: wrap; }
    .svc-hero-visual {
      position: relative;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      min-height: 340px;
    }
    .svc-hero-visual img {
      width: min(400px, 100%);
      filter: drop-shadow(0 16px 24px rgba(4,31,58,.12));
    }
    .svc-feature-badges {
      position: absolute;
      bottom: 0;
      left: 0;
      right: 0;
      display: flex;
      justify-content: center;
      gap: 16px;
    }
    .svc-feature-badges span {
      display: grid;
      place-items: center;
      width: 72px;
      height: 72px;
      border-radius: 50%;
      background: #003d7c;
      color: #fff;
      text-align: center;
      font-size: 13px;
      font-weight: 800;
      line-height: 1.3;
      box-shadow: 0 8px 18px rgba(0,61,124,.18);
    }

    /* ====================================================
       サービス4カード
       ==================================================== */
    .svc-cards {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr);
      gap: 16px;
    }
    .svc-card {
      position: relative;
      background: #fff;
      border: 1px solid #dce7f2;
      border-radius: 8px;
      padding: 32px 24px 24px;
      min-height: 420px;
      box-shadow: 0 12px 30px rgba(3,34,70,.08);
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
    }
    .svc-num {
      position: absolute;
      top: 18px;
      left: 16px;
      width: 44px;
      height: 44px;
      border-radius: 50%;
      background: #003b78;
      color: #fff;
      font-size: 14px;
      font-weight: 800;
      display: grid;
      place-items: center;
    }
    .svc-card-icon {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      height: 120px;
      margin: 0 auto 16px;
    }
    .svc-card-icon img {
      max-height: 120px;
      width: auto;
      object-fit: contain;
    }
    .svc-card h3 {
      font-size: 19px;
      font-weight: 800;
      text-align: center;
      color: #063f7e;
      margin: 0 0 10px;
      line-height: 1.4;
    }
    .svc-card > p {
      font-size: 15px;
      font-weight: 700;
      color: #111;
      margin: 0 0 14px;
    }
    .svc-card ul {
      list-style: none;
      padding: 0;
      margin: 0;
      flex: 1;
    }
    .svc-card li {
      position: relative;
      font-size: 15px;
      line-height: 1.8;
      padding-left: 22px;
      color: #123;
    }
    .svc-card li::before {
      content: "✓";
      position: absolute;
      left: 0;
      top: 3px;
      width: 14px;
      height: 14px;
      border-radius: 50%;
      background: #0b56a6;
      color: #fff;
      font-size: 9px;
      display: grid;
      place-items: center;
    }
    .svc-card a {
      display: block;
      text-align: center;
      color: #0b4a93;
      font-size: 15px;
      font-weight: 900;
    }
    .svc-card a:hover { text-decoration: underline; }

    /* ====================================================
       対応業種
       ==================================================== */
    .svc-industry {
      background: #f4f8fc;
    }
    .industry-box {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(6, 1fr);
      border: 1px solid #dce7f2;
      border-radius: 8px;
      overflow: hidden;
      background: #fff;
    }
    .industry-item {
      text-align: center;
      padding: 22px 12px 18px;
      border-right: 1px solid #dce7f2;
    }
    .industry-item:last-child { border-right: 0; }
    .industry-item .ind-icon {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      height: 64px;
      margin: 0 auto 12px;
    }
    .industry-item .ind-icon img {
      max-height: 64px;
      width: auto;
      object-fit: contain;
    }
    .industry-item strong { display: block; font-size: 15px; color: #003b78; font-weight: 800; margin-bottom: 6px; }
    .industry-item small  { display: block; font-size: 13px; color: #5b6c7f; line-height: 1.7; }
    .svc-note { text-align: center; color: #33516e; font-size: 14px; margin: 14px 0 0; }

    /* ====================================================
       開発の流れ
       ==================================================== */
    .flow-list {
      display: flex;
      align-items: flex-start;
      background: #fff;
      border: 1px solid #dce7f2;
      border-radius: 8px;
      padding: 28px 8px;
      gap: 0;
    }
    .flow-step {
      flex: 1;
      min-width: 0;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      align-items: center;
      text-align: center;
      padding: 0 4px;
      position: relative;
    }
    .flow-step-num {
      display: grid;
      place-items: center;
      width: 36px;
      height: 36px;
      border-radius: 50%;
      background: #0b56a6;
      color: #fff;
      font-size: 13px;
      font-weight: 800;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
      flex-shrink: 0;
    }
    .flow-step-img {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      height: 80px;
      margin-bottom: 12px;
    }
    .flow-step-img img {
      max-height: 80px;
      width: auto;
      object-fit: contain;
    }
    .flow-step strong { display: block; color: #063f7e; font-size: 14px; font-weight: 800; margin-bottom: 4px; }
    .flow-step small  { display: block; font-size: 12px; color: #5b6c7f; line-height: 1.6; }
    .flow-arrow {
      flex-shrink: 0;
      align-self: center;
      margin-top: -44px;
      color: #a8b9ca;
      font-size: 14px;
      padding: 0;
    }
    .flow-message {
      width: min(760px, 100%);
      margin: 16px auto 0;
      padding: 12px 20px;
      border: 1px solid #b9d6ee;
      background: #f0f8ff;
      border-radius: 7px;
      text-align: center;
      color: #0b4a93;
      font-size: 16px;
      font-weight: 700;
    }

    /* ====================================================
       料金の目安
       ==================================================== */
    .svc-price-section {
      background: #fafbfc;
      padding: 48px 0;
    }
    .svc-price-section h2 { text-align: left; margin-bottom: 24px; }
    .price-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
      gap: 18px;
    }
    .price-card {
      min-height: 200px;
      border-radius: 9px;
      padding: 28px 38px;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: space-between;
      overflow: hidden;
    }
    .price-card.blue  { background: linear-gradient(90deg, #edf7ff, #f9fcff); }
    .price-card.green { background: linear-gradient(90deg, #f0fbf3, #f9fff8); }
    .price-card h3 { color: #0a4a99; font-size: 22px; font-weight: 800; margin: 0; }
    .price-card.green h3 { color: #2a7b43; }
    .price-card .price {
      font-size: 34px;
      color: #0a4a99;
      margin: 4px 0;
      font-weight: 800;
      white-space: nowrap;
    }
    .price-card.green .price { color: #2a7b43; }
    .price-card .price strong { font-size: 58px; line-height: 1; font-weight: 900; }
    .price-card small { display: block; color: #444; margin-bottom: 10px; font-size: 14px; }
    .price-card p:not(.price) { font-size: 15px; margin: 0; line-height: 1.7; }
    .price-card .price-img { max-width: 185px; opacity: .85; flex-shrink: 0; }
    .price-card .shield { max-width: 190px; opacity: .42; transform: translate(20px, 4px); flex-shrink: 0; }
    .price-footnote { text-align: center; color: #244668; font-size: 14px; margin: 12px 0 0; }
    @media (max-width: 760px) {
      .price-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
      .price-card { padding: 24px; flex-direction: column; align-items: flex-start; }
    }

    /* ====================================================
       CTA
       ==================================================== */
    .svc-cta {
      background: linear-gradient(90deg, #003a78, #004c99);
      color: #fff;
      padding: 40px 0;
    }
    .svc-cta-inner {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 80px 1fr auto;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 28px;
    }
    .svc-cta-icon {
      width: 70px;
      height: 70px;
      border-radius: 50%;
      background: rgba(255,255,255,.18);
      display: grid;
      place-items: center;
      font-size: 32px;
    }
    .svc-cta h2 {
      text-align: left;
      color: #fff;
      font-size: 28px;
      margin: 0 0 4px;
    }
    .svc-cta p { margin: 0; font-size: 15px; color: rgba(255,255,255,.85); }

    /* ====================================================
       レスポンシブ
       ==================================================== */
    @media (max-width: 1040px) {
      .svc-hero-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
      .svc-hero { background: #F8F8F6; }
      .svc-hero-visual { min-height: auto; padding-bottom: 80px; }
      .svc-cards { grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr); }
      .industry-box { grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr); }
      .industry-item:nth-child(3n) { border-right: 0; }
      .flow-list { flex-wrap: wrap; }
      .flow-step { flex: 0 0 calc(33.333% - 16px); }
      .flow-arrow:nth-child(4), .flow-arrow:nth-child(8) { display: none; }
    }
    @media (max-width: 760px) {
      .svc-hero { padding-top: 40px; }
      .svc-hero h1 { font-size: 28px; }
      .sp-only { display: inline; }
      .svc-hero .lead { font-size: 17px; }
      .svc-hero-points { flex-direction: column; gap: 12px; }
      .svc-hero-actions { flex-direction: column; }
      .svc-hero-actions .btn { width: 100%; }
      .svc-cards { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
      .industry-box { grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; }
      .industry-item { border-bottom: 1px solid #dce7f2; }
      .industry-item:nth-child(odd) { border-right: 1px solid #dce7f2; }
      .industry-item:nth-child(2n) { border-right: 0; }
      .flow-list { flex-direction: column; align-items: center; }
      .flow-step { flex: 0 0 auto; width: 100%; max-width: 300px; margin: 12px 0; }
      .flow-arrow:nth-child(4), .flow-arrow:nth-child(8) { display: flex; }
      .flow-arrow { margin-top: 0; transform: rotate(90deg); }
      .svc-cta-inner { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
      .svc-cta-icon { display: none; }
    }
  </style>

  <!--/* ヒーロー */-->
  <section class="svc-hero">
    <div class="container svc-hero-grid">
      <div class="svc-hero-copy">
        <h1 class="svc-hero-h1">BizSysで<br class="sp-only"><span>解決できること</span></h1>
        <p class="lead" style="font-size:17px;">
          現場のムダ・手間・ミスを減らし、<br>
          業務を見える化・自動化・効率化する<br>
          システムを開発します。
        </p>
        <div class="svc-hero-points">
          <div class="svc-point">
            <strong>見える化</strong>
            <small>データを一元管理</small>
          </div>
          <div class="svc-point">
            <strong>自動化</strong>
            <small>手作業を削減</small>
          </div>
          <div class="svc-point">
            <strong>属人化解消</strong>
            <small>誰でも使える仕組みに</small>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="svc-hero-actions">
          <a class="btn primary" href="/contact/">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" style="margin:2px 5px 0 0" width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M4 4h16c1.1 0 2 .9 2 2v12c0 1.1-.9 2-2 2H4c-1.1 0-2-.9-2-2V6c0-1.1.9-2 2-2z"></path><polyline points="22,6 12,13 2,6"></polyline></svg>          
            無料相談する
          </a>
          <a class="btn secondary" href="/cases/">導入事例を見る</a>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="svc-hero-visual">
        <img src="/images/hero-dashboard.png" alt="業務システムのダッシュボード画面" style="width:min(400px,100%);height:auto;display:block;">
        <div class="svc-feature-badges">
          <span>一元<br>管理</span>
          <span>自動化</span>
          <span>リアル<br>タイム</span>
          <span>共有<br>連携</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!--/* サービス内容4カード */-->
  <section class="svc-section">
    <div class="container">
      <h2>サービス内容</h2>
      <div class="svc-cards">
        <article class="svc-card">
          <span class="svc-num">01</span>
          <div class="svc-card-icon">
            <img src="/images/svc-icon1.png" alt="Excel管理からの脱却">
          </div>
          <h3>Excel管理からの脱却</h3>
          <p>Excelやスプレッドシートでの管理を、使いやすいシステムに。</p>
          <ul>
            <li>案件管理</li>
            <li>顧客管理</li>
            <li>在庫管理</li>
            <li>売上管理</li>
            <li>請求管理 など</li>
          </ul>
        </article>
        <article class="svc-card">
          <span class="svc-num">02</span>
          <div class="svc-card-icon">
            <img src="/images/svc-icon2.png" alt="業務の自動化">
          </div>
          <h3>業務の自動化</h3>
          <p>手作業や転記作業を自動化し、ミスを減らし生産性を向上。</p>
          <ul>
            <li>CSV取込・出力</li>
            <li>データ連携</li>
            <li>自動集計・レポート</li>
            <li>メール・LINE通知</li>
            <li>定型業務の自動化 など</li>
          </ul>
        </article>
        <article class="svc-card">
          <span class="svc-num">03</span>
          <div class="svc-card-icon">
            <img src="/images/svc-icon3.png" alt="現場向けWebシステム">
          </div>
          <h3>現場向けWebシステム</h3>
          <p>現場で使いやすいWebシステムをオーダーメイドで開発。</p>
          <ul>
            <li>モバイル・タブレット対応</li>
            <li>進捗管理</li>
            <li>情報共有</li>
            <li>権限管理</li>
            <li>外部システム連携 など</li>
          </ul>
        </article>
        <article class="svc-card">
          <span class="svc-num">04</span>
          <div class="svc-card-icon">
            <img src="/images/svc-icon4.png" alt="保守・運用サポート">
          </div>
          <h3>保守・運用サポート</h3>
          <p>導入後も安心して使えるように、継続的なサポートを提供。</p>
          <ul>
            <li>不具合対応</li>
            <li>機能追加・改善</li>
            <li>運用相談</li>
            <li>定期メンテナンス</li>
            <li>システムの安定運用</li>
          </ul>
        </article>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!--/* 対応業種 */-->
  <section class="svc-section svc-industry">
    <div class="container">
      <h2>対応業種・業務の一例</h2>
      <div class="industry-box">
        <div class="industry-item">
          <div class="ind-icon">
            <img src="/images/industries/ind1-truck.png" alt="物流・運送業">
          </div>
          <strong>物流・運送業</strong>
          <small>配車管理・発注管理・<br>在庫管理・ドライバー管理など</small>
        </div>
        <div class="industry-item">
          <div class="ind-icon">
            <img src="/images/industries/ind2-medical.png" alt="医療・介護・福祉">
          </div>
          <strong>医療・介護・福祉</strong>
          <small>記録管理・シフト管理・<br>連絡共有・請求管理など</small>
        </div>
        <div class="industry-item">
          <div class="ind-icon">
            <img src="/images/industries/ind3-cart.png" alt="EC・小売">
          </div>
          <strong>EC・小売</strong>
          <small>在庫連携・受注管理・<br>商品分析・出品管理など</small>
        </div>
        <div class="industry-item">
          <div class="ind-icon">
            <img src="/images/industries/ind4-factory.png" alt="製造業">
          </div>
          <strong>製造業</strong>
          <small>見積管理・工程管理・<br>在庫管理・品質管理など</small>
        </div>
        <div class="industry-item">
          <div class="ind-icon">
            <img src="/images/industries/ind5-car.png" alt="レンタカー・サービス業">
          </div>
          <strong>レンタカー・サービス業</strong>
          <small>予約管理・車両管理・<br>請求管理・点検管理など</small>
        </div>
        <div class="industry-item">
          <div class="ind-icon">
            <img src="/images/industries/ind6-other.png" alt="その他の業種">
          </div>
          <strong>その他の業種</strong>
          <small>学校・団体・イベント・<br>不動産・建設業 など</small>
        </div>
      </div>
      <p class="svc-note">上記以外の業種・業務にも幅広く対応しています。まずはお気軽にご相談ください。</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!--/* 開発の流れ */-->
  <section class="svc-section">
    <div class="container">
      <h2>開発の流れ</h2>
      <div class="flow-list">
        <div class="flow-step">
          <span class="flow-step-num">01</span>
          <div class="flow-step-img"><img src="/images/flow/flow1.png" alt="ご相談"></div>
          <strong>ご相談</strong>
          <small>現状の課題やご要望をヒアリングします。</small>
        </div>
        <div class="flow-arrow">▶</div>
        <div class="flow-step">
          <span class="flow-step-num">02</span>
          <div class="flow-step-img"><img src="/images/flow/flow2.png" alt="課題の整理・ご提案"></div>
          <strong>課題の整理・ご提案</strong>
          <small>業務を整理し、最適なシステムをご提案します。</small>
        </div>
        <div class="flow-arrow">▶</div>
        <div class="flow-step">
          <span class="flow-step-num">03</span>
          <div class="flow-step-img"><img src="/images/flow/flow3.png" alt="お見積り"></div>
          <strong>お見積り</strong>
          <small>ご要望に合わせたお見積りを提示します。</small>
        </div>
        <div class="flow-arrow">▶</div>
        <div class="flow-step">
          <span class="flow-step-num">04</span>
          <div class="flow-step-img"><img src="/images/flow/flow4.png" alt="開発・テスト"></div>
          <strong>開発・テスト</strong>
          <small>設計・開発・テストを経て使いやすく構築します。</small>
        </div>
        <div class="flow-arrow">▶</div>
        <div class="flow-step">
          <span class="flow-step-num">05</span>
          <div class="flow-step-img"><img src="/images/flow/flow5.png" alt="運用開始"></div>
          <strong>運用開始</strong>
          <small>スムーズに運用開始。</small>
        </div>
        <div class="flow-arrow">▶</div>
        <div class="flow-step">
          <span class="flow-step-num">06</span>
          <div class="flow-step-img"><img src="/images/flow/flow6.png" alt="保守・改善"></div>
          <strong>保守・改善</strong>
          <small>運用後も継続サポートを行います。</small>
        </div>
      </div>
